description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. FrogSlayer Studios presents, Go, an ancient Chinese game of strategy now available on XBox Live Community Games.  Learn to play with our interactive tutorial and then play against your friends locally or against players at all skill levels via XBox Live.  For more information vist us at www.FrogSlayerStudios.com
